  Locus:
    Page: 243
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Heaven & Hell
---
Heaven and hell are states of being. Heaven is being in harmony with God’s
will; hell is being out of harmony with God’s will. You can be in either
state on either side of life. There is no permanent hell. ... Heaven is
only one thought away.
